{"tid":1661672,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國參議員卡丁：參議院現在必須拿香港人權與民主法案上大會","createTime":"2019-10-18T08:51:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-19T03:48:33.000Z","uid":70063,"like":455,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"d796965a0880d34f22b83cd7a15d8df50beecad5","tid":1661672,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T08:51:17.000Z","msg":"I&rsquo;m pleased that the House passed the Hong Kong Human Rights and Democracy Act yesterday. The Senate must take up our bill now. <br />\n<br />\nAs basic human rights in #HongKong continue to be trampled on by the Chinese, we must speak up with one, united voice in defense of democracy.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenatorCardin/status/1184855665719894016?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenatorCardin%2Fstatus%2F1184855665719894016%3Fs%3D19&d=JQdTOMZ4NvWA5L1F4kLiz02FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=eac2d197\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenatorCardin%2Fstatus%2F1184855665719894016%3Fs%3D19&h=30f87783\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SenatorCardin/status/1184855665719894016?s=19</a>"},{"pid":"6302f24da041b0d1390b5432af6d4dfca829610e","tid":1661672,"uid":249263,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T08:51:58.000Z","msg":"大家記得要響twitter 同美國講條bill好重要<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好咁老定！<br />\n去twitter多謝人地支持，<br />\n講香港真係好需要條Bill啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n#hongkonghumanrightsanddemocracyact <br />\n#standwithhongkong<br />\n#fightforfreedom<br />\n<br />\n留意番Representatives 同Senator係有分別，<br />\n望清楚其他人點叫人先好！<br />\n唔好叫人First Name！<br />\n外媒報條Bill 的新聞都好重要！<br />\nretweet哂佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\ntwitter 組已經將議員/人權法新聞的tweets<br />\n放左入bot task1<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=JQdTOMZ4NvWA5L1F4kLiz02FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=97102158\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">入<span style=\"color: violet;\"> /task1</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後咪撚再串錯hongkong!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d919be2055704d1d6e0a8ecfb09edbee839a774","tid":1661672,"uid":74586,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T08:52:24.000Z","msg":"sir this way<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n去like and retweet先"},{"pid":"e41faf8519c6d6b1e04c948fbcca5b640eed0fa5","tid":1661672,"uid":312125,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T08:53:04.000Z","msg":"可能會卡在麥康奈爾手上，佢老婆係支那人<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/cTvTisEoEpw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FcTvTisEoEpw&d=JQdTOMZ4NvWA5L1F4kLiz02FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=b2744fd0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/cTvTisEoEpw</a><br />\n<br />\n【FC】西九站遊行係中共真春袋！<span style=\"color: red;\">需要針對強國文宣<strong>輸出革命</strong></span>！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1661232\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1661232</a><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>消息人士表示，7月7日過10萬人去到高鐵西九龍站後，「中國國家安全委員會」就對西九龍站「突發」事件設定了「專案」，就各種事況的發生計劃了處理辦法。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n輸出革命文宣圖：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/akqjfDV\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/akqjfDV</a><br />\n<br />\n呢度仲有一單近期爆出嘅關於中共高層貪污嘅核彈新聞，直刺中共心臟，希望都可以唸辦法向強國人宣傳一下<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/mDLryDX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/mDLryDX</a>"},{"pid":"6c233bdce5b5d00dda2bf39dcf6a6341c5ba4fff","tid":1661672,"uid":9049,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T08:53:29.000Z","msg":"區議會選舉專題研究之抗爭Project<br />\n引導香港-啟蒙運動：<br />\n-點Push更多人投票？<br />\n-何謂民主、自由、公義、法治、公平？<br />\n-以上普世價值對大眾有咩好處？<br />\n-香港未來如何向前走？<br />\n<br />\n學習任務：<br />\n1.了解西方啓蒙運動前因後果<br />\n2.Search民主、自由、公義、法治、公平<br />\n3.將普世價值連結到香港人利益利益利益<br />\n4.走向獨裁/走向民主，主權在民<br />\n5.睇一次基本法<br />\n6.睇埋選舉條例<br />\n<br />\n活動：<br />\n民主小天使：和理傾<br />\n落街、落區、開攤位、教育關心街坊<br />\nConnect學歷較低、新移民、淺藍選民<br />\n口號：愛民主，黎投票；撐自由，齊發聲<br />\n            為公義，企出黎；護法治，三分權<br />\n            要公平，改制度；港未來，自己來<br />\n<br />\n我相信極權唔怕武力升級，卻怕頭腦升級，有更多人看穿一切的謊言，群起反抗！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Signature</span>簽名檔：守護香港，深層改革<br />\nVersion 2019.10.17 <span style=\"color: red;\"><em>愛民主，黎投票</em></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">Be Water! Be Smart!</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">注意事項</span></span>⚠️：<br />\n洞察政府現時策略：<br />\n1. 相信政府透過中間人搵pro-Beijing people/黑社會襲擊示威者&gt;煽動群眾暴力&gt;警察暴力鎮壓<br />\n2. 政府透過示威者=破壞，政府=復修，改善形象<br />\n3. 轉移視線，避談不公義嘅制度<br />\n4. 警方扮好人，想洗底<br />\n5. 開始將部分示威者塑造為恐怖分子，增強鎮壓說服力<br />\n<br />\n連登五毛滲透嚴重，大家要帶腦睇post<br />\n<br />\n政府損失：0人，民望、信譽跌至谷底<br />\n香港人損失：2363人+多人曾經活著<br />\n<br />\n抗爭轉型及進化建議：<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">持久戰拖垮邪惡</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">重要目標：</span></strong>11月24號區議會選舉<br />\n香港民主及人權法案<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">防範：</span></strong>掌心雷、利誘淺黃淺藍市民、抹黑<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">流水式示威：</span></strong>警察舉旗咪去另一個地方示威，香港咁多地方可以去，佢想捉你，你咪話走緊囉，太多人行得慢好正常，合情合理合法！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">適當武力/自衛反擊：</span></strong>合情又合理！<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\"><strong>游擊戰？：</strong></span>對抗黑社會/恐怖分子（文宣解釋）<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">創意活動：抗爭融入生活</span></strong>唱歌比賽？跑步大叫？商場罷買？摺紙？18區和你傾、流水式返學返工#Shout4HK#諗到再加<br />\n<br />\n公平、自由、民主、公義、人權<span style=\"color: gold;\">得來不易</span><br />\n漫長的道路上需要<span style=\"color: gold;\">你支持我，我扶持你</span><br />\n有時惘然若失，但我們也要<span style=\"color: gold;\">自信往前邁步</span><br />\n有咩嘢唔想失去，就努力<span style=\"color: gold;\">捍衛</span>同<span style=\"color: gold;\">守護</span><br />\n現在就用自己雙手實踐夢想，<span style=\"color: gold;\">迎接未來</span><br />\n<br />\n短期目標：保持民意、減少被捕<br />\n建議：落街和你傾，落區啦！文宣！<br />\n中期目標：區議會(94%民主產生)<br />\n建議：關注身邊人，團結一致，各有各做<br />\n長期目標：強化黃色陣營、黃色經濟圈<br />\n建議：抗爭生活化，減少比錢極權陣營<br />\n終極目標：民選議會、民選政府<br />\n建議：國際戰線、啓蒙思想、人滅心不滅<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">公務員</span></strong>：小隱於野，中隱於市，大隱於朝<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>和勇合一</strong></span>：1.合法之下，最大勇武<br />\n                     2. 做任何事，永不被捕<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">@謠言係疫症&bull;不傳播&bull;去求診&bull;澄清藥<br />\n@FakeNews係Cancer&bull;不擴散&bull;求事實&bull;割<br />\n@接觸資訊時，腦袋要清醒</span><br />\n<br />\n只要爭取民主團火未熄，還是有機會達成<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">衛城革命，生活抗爭</span><br />\n@<span style=\"color: orange;\">Template</span>@<br />\n<strong><em>升級技能/能力值</em></strong>：1. 讀書、識法律2.運動、鬥長命3.和勇合一精神4.批判性思考5.專業技能<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XMdiioB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXMdiioB.jpg&h=7e10cb33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持；Best effort，你呢？民主尚未成功，同志仍需努力<br />\n@<span style=\"color: orange;\">Template</span>@<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">要記住極權如何打壓示威：</span></strong><br />\n1.抹黑：利用少部分的暴力衝突而將全部示威者形容為「邪惡」、示威=港獨、新華社、環球時報、人民日報<br />\n2.誤導：警總救護車、雷射槍、9吋尖刀等等<br />\n3.滲透：5毛、陳雲、黃x民、譚香文<br />\n4.假民意/曲解民意：主流民意是......<br />\n5.5毛輿論-分化、負面、fake news、煽動手足做負效益/低效益工作<br />\n6.強迫企業自我審查<br />\n7.出動黑社會、愛國暴徒<br />\n8.扮示威者：(負面的)破壞eg.遊行<br />\n9.嫁禍示威者/黑警：打議員打記者打女仔<br />\n10.扮好人/扮對話：「江山易改本性難移」<br />\n11.警察濫權、濫捕、暴力執法、恐嚇<br />\n12.利用親中人士發表「假」權威言論<br />\n13.高樓價掠奪民脂民膏<br />\n14.矮化示威者為甲由、yellow object<br />\n15.假對話，真緊急法：獨裁者2.0<br />\n16.高壓統治，嚇到你噤聲<br />\n17.黑社會X警方X中聯辦X政府X地產霸權<br />\n諗到再加</span><br />\nSir, my concern is not whether God is on our side; my greatest concern is to be on God's side, for God is always right."},{"pid":"480fa25f96ec685da23bd33365981a03095f4395","tid":1661672,"uid":197086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T08:57:55.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1cd0868164cd5572f90c81bf9c3d807eebb6ad90","tid":1661672,"uid":32221,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T09:00:53.000Z","msg":"好似愈黎愈多唔同既senator 出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8119bd72aabe247d1964b16290496d129adbbd7","tid":1661672,"uid":181088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T09:07:02.000Z","msg":"就咁睇既話唔係好差<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44e0939c00fa127ba1107e68d9da9ff0aaec29af","tid":1661672,"uid":192824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T09:11:25.000Z","msg":"癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1a574b705693898164084148edc3822e1450a9d","tid":1661672,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T09:13:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91e46e8fd96c9037fc28aa74333f31be7c404e2c","tid":1661672,"uid":48735,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T09:17:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a09f0f56ce0aa1c7bbd4abf55e421549c21c838","tid":1661672,"uid":170143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T09:20:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gi